background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">)</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>Drop into <code>~/.bashrc</code>. Replace <code>xdg-open</code> with <code>open</code> on macOS.</p>
<p>The fzf snippet stays out of the Python package on purpose — <code>xdg-open</code>/<code>open</code> is environment-specific, fzf isn’t a Python dep, and shell composition is what shells are good at. yttoc generates the data; your shell does the searching.</p>
</section>
